{
  "text": "Our dependent variable is the absolute number of new plant transactions identified in the International Trade Administration publications from each year between 1989 and 1994. In their state-level study, [CITATION_1] use similar data covering 1977 to 1988. Glickman and Woodward (1987) also use this data source for 1979 to 1983.",
